    <item>
      <title>Clarc v1.2.0</title>
      <sparkle:version>16</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 08:01:55 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
<h3>New</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Independent font size controls for the interface and the message area — adjust each separately in Settings.</li>
  <li>Auto-preview toggles for pasted images and dropped files, so you can decide when attachments preview automatically.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Improved</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Blockquotes now render as a single continuous vertical bar instead of breaking between lines.</li>
  <li>Links open directly in your default browser, skipping the macOS link popup.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
  <li>An error bubble now appears when a response stream ends without producing any visible output, so failed turns are no longer silent.</li>
</ul>
      ]]></description>
