      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 06:15:08 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Resolve <code>env: node: No such file or directory</code> error when starting a chat. The app now reads the user's shell <code>PATH</code> so the bundled <code>claude</code> CLI can locate <code>node</code> regardless of where it was installed (Homebrew, nvm, npm-global). (#8)</li>
</ul>
      ]]></description>
